Package: eventb-checker
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre-headless | java-runtime-headless, ${misc:Depends}
Description: standalone type checker for Event-B models
 eventb-checker validates Event-B models (.bum/.buc/.eventb files or zip
 archives exported from Rodin) and reports type-checking errors without a Rodin
 installation.
 .
 It is distributed as a self-contained Java archive and is convenient for use in
 continuous integration and command-line workflows.
